              <h2>Treatment</h2>
              <p>
                 The treatment for Bladder cancer includes radiation therapy, chemotherapy and surgery. While surgery and radiation therapy aim at getting rid of the cancerous cells alone the chemotherapy is a more systemic treatment and can kill cancer cells in any part of the body.
